Blessed to be honoured on this Mother's day by @feaglobal and @manishaguptasns .

Sometimes I doubt wht i am doing , specially with the failures i face, changing relations i see or the struggles that come in the way !! Sometimes it's very anxiety giving too. But such recognitions keep me going and give me the boost i need to believe i am on the right track. 

Every mother is doing her best in her own way, never doubt her intentions !! Don't judge her for her choices , whether she chooses to work from home, work at home, or work at office. Respect her work, her choices, just let her be, coz only she knows the best for child 🚸
.

Underpants from @thecoverupproject . Super soft and comfortable . Also you can customise your own underpants with the stickers coming with the box.
 You just need to cut the sticker, place it on the underpants. Place a heated iron on it for about 1 min and than let it cool down for atleast 2-3 mins . After cooling down remove the plastic and voila your kids underpants with his/ fav cartoon is ready. It’s available for both boys and girls for up to 9 years age group.

Now available at @lovecovera
